title: 09/10 Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 1 Recap - QB Concerns?
description:
David Johnson is hurt and it was not a good week for QBs, but it was a great week for Matthew Stafford (8:22), Leonard Fournette (10:00) and Amari Cooper (12:00) among others. Jamey gives his thoughts on Week 1 ... We play Buy or Sell with Aaron Rodgers (20:48), Tarik Cohen (23:50), Ty Montgomery (25:32), Kenny Golladay, Cooper Kupp (30:00) and more ... Thoughts on every game (33:10)! Drop Andy Dalton? Add Charles Clay? Are we concerned about the TEN or ATL offenses? ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
